Place the peach into the fridge then take it out.

Place the peach on the left side of the sink.

high_descs: Walk out of the bedroom into the hallway, turn right then continue into the living room and walk over to the coffeetable between the sofa chairs.
Pick up the peach from the side table.
Walk out of the living room, down the hall, into the kitchen on the right, and up to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator door, place the peach on the left side of the bottom shelf that is below the other apple, shut the door, and then retrieve the peach and close the door again.
Turn around and walk over to the sink.
Place the peach on the edge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Cool off a peach in the refrigerator to set on the sink.
